      "lineNumber": 1,
      "text": "Office Mem... UNITED ... GOVERNMENT",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 2,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 3,
      "text": "TO : DIRECTOR, FBI (62-83894) DATE: MARCH 21, 1952",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 4,
      "text": "FROM : SAC, CHICAGO (100-18999)",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 5,
      "text": "SUBJECT: FLYING DISCS",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "text": "[REDACTED] INFORMANT",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "Mr. [REDACTED] an artist living at [REDACTED]",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "Chicago, Illinois [REDACTED] advised SA [REDACTED]",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "on March 11, 1952 that he saw a flying disc at 9:00 AM on March",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "6, 1952.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "[REDACTED] stated that he was looking out of a window at his home",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "which window faces south, when he saw a flying disc at approximately",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "7,000 feet above Fullerton Avenue. The angle of elevation of the",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "disc above the horizon was about 45 degrees. The disc came out",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "of a cloud in the east, stopped and hung motionless in mid-air",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "for a split second, then flew due south at great speed.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "He described the disc as approximately six feet in diameter, circular,",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "white in color with a bluish tinge. The disc, he said, appeared to",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "have been constructed out of a metal similar to aluminum. He also",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "stated that he saw no exhaust, lights, or heard no sound connected",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "with its movements. He noted nothing on it as to how it could maintain",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "its even flight and believed it to have been radio controlled. He",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "said it disappeared out of sight in approximately three seconds,",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "estimating the speed at 600-700 miles per hour or more. He said it",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "went so fast it appeared to flutter. When the disc disappeared from",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "sight it was about the size of a golf ball on the southern horizon.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "[REDACTED] made a sketch of the disc and the sketch and the above",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "information were furnished to the local office of the Office of",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "Special Investigations.",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
